title: Christina Jensen
text:
Christina Jensen (born ) was a female Danish <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Goalkeeper%20%28association%20football%29">goalkeeper</a>.
She was part of the <a href="Denmark%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Denmark women's national football team</a> at the <a href="Football%20at%20the%201996%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20tournament">1996 Summer Olympics</a>, but did not play.
She participated in the <a href="1999%20FIFA%20Women%27s%20World%20Cup">1999 FIFA Women's World Cup</a>.
